Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球的馮·布朗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受重創的1號機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了療傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在母親般的阿納海姆中躺臥著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失在乘員眼前的宏·浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在最下層的凱利相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想重當機師的凱利的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震撼了浦木的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而當浦木找回自我之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重生的GUNDAM出現在他眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\fs60}藍耀的火焰中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50}{\t(\fscx200 \fscy200) \fad(500,500)}650
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50}{\t(\fscx200 \fscy200) \fad(500,500)}700
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50}{\t(\fscx200 \fscy200) \fad(500,500)}750
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50}{\t(\fscx200 \fscy200) \fad(500,500)}800
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態良好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒出現G Clutter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}G Clutter：重力干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:02:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50}{\t(\fscx200 \fscy200) \fad(500,500)}900
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就比模擬提升了115%的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與追加助推器的適應性也是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏也總算恢復正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full Burnern測試項目完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返航
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致動壓縮機釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維護模式設定OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對GUNDAM各部位進行應力分析
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full Burnern如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定發揮到160
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,160？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的機體能提升到230哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做的話我會撐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連淋浴也無法享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架GUNDAM是我精心調整的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.32,0:04:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起可真是不會覺得悶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.15,0:04:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知何時才能上岸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你、你在看著啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這個，真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.05,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如中學裏的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.43,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀妮娜一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi，摩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉、吉斯你何時…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏，戰況是千變萬化的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再慢吞吞的話你會被孤立的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦裏不是也有那樣的好人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被騙了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰爭還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉托拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再提醒一次，在月球引起騷動我很難辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說不在月球就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默許我們迪拉茲艦隊的崛起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓世間陷於混沌的就是像你這樣的月球住民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想為希瑪大人略盡綿力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼能再給我更好點的MS嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是給了聯邦好東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要是有即將出廠的MS的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣讓雙方一直擁有對等的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，那艘阿爾比昂太礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你別太幫他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛是盲目的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿爾比昂出航前還留下好多事沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還要上船？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的GUNDAM的數據才更重要吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拚命的大冒險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是大戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是公司的命令嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面並沒有那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但確實提到過要把你調離MS開發部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不乘聯邦的船也能做研究吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也受你雙親所托，有責任照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那艘船肯定會和迪拉茲艦隊交戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層人士似乎希望他們快點離開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連好好考慮的時間也不給我了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也是一直如此支撐著家庭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧你一天就完成到運行狀態了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙太驚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是約定好的東西，收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在加入迪拉茲艦隊之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事必須先解決
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話拉托拉也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏，就當做貨款收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備大尉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就任金嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會的話會讓我為難的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用來拜託你不讓我要搭乘的這架MA出差錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪大人是帶我來擔任它的機師的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒淪落到要特地將機動兵器交給獨臂的人來駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕不是恭維話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待著你的復職
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們東山再起的時刻來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話只告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近日內我將為某個目的降落到地球的澳大利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而屆時你也將聽到迪拉茲閣下的號召
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲土重來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再像所羅門那時一樣並肩作戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你好好響應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給親愛的凱利·雷茲那大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿納貝爾·卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙現在在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星塵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是迪拉茲艦隊的作戰代號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他們現在的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是為了引開我們注意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其關鍵或許就在被奪的GUNDAM2號機身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天阿爾比昂將在21時啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為索敵攻擊部隊向所羅門海域出動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但請全員做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位或許也隱約感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因月球方面的要求所引響
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，對此不能抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球的人們與我們的立場不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜不是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我有哪裏不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過第3浮標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左轉舵5度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉為自力航行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左轉舵5度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，我在三號街找到家好店…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人哦，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好、好乾淨的工作場所啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉色不好，出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，找我有急事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下來行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的空調溫度高了點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點熱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起航前有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太忙的話就算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作已結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是、是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這還是第一次…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…這、這次的機械手自動系統的脈衝…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…噪音似乎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噪音怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、不…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只懂駕駛MS嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有的是時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.45,0:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利，你在裏面吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了，凱利！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你諒解，拉托拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.70,0:15:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒GUNDAM的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能得到認同了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多久沒見喬西亞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙也長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我討厭電視電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也算見過面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新安特瓦普也不是壞地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把臉露出來好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？你母親也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽課長說你上了聯邦的軍艦時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擔心不知會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:15:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該棄權了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希瑪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3宇宙港的閉鎖被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要接收VAL-WALO的廢港嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}VAL-WALO：一年戰爭後期ZION的MA，MA-05的後繼機\N是對戰艦和對MS近戰兩用型的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太早了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭多事的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那、那不是MA嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出港前10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜為什麼沒來？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼對待她的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜不乘這艘船了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來拿行李的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把原因、請把原因告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵MA接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘員以外的人請盡速離艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘員以外的人請盡速離艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MA？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利·雷茲那也腦筋燒壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希瑪不找他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要帶著MA向聯邦投降嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我以一架ZAKU去阻擋MA嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爛攤子就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算拼了命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟對自己人攻擊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對自己人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說外面有戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在通信呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凱利·雷茲那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦的船聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和GUNDAM決一勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各MS快準備出動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎擊戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止主動攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是MA嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉，為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向0-8-7
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被認為我們是把馮·布朗當作盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0-6-3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向0-6-3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS還沒準備好？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11時方向！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人開炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和什麼GM交手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派GUNDAM出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則就攻擊馮·布朗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指名要GUNDAM嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM Full Burnern可以出動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給浦木少尉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉，GUNDAM出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了啊，GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利先生，為何要做這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浦木嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你駕駛GUNDAM？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是遲早的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧，凱利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了，浦木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的狀況是無法選擇的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說外面在戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要在這種地方打？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打的話在宇宙或地球就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，這裏封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要封鎖了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:20:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把性命都要賭上的目的，究竟有什麼價值？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪拉茲閣下應當已陳述過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對士兵來說鬥爭本能才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啞彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥不是生就是死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要出動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，凱利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.37,0:22:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事讓卡多去做就夠了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止這種大地球主義的單挑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.73,0:22:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家互相忍耐一下就沒事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜小姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒打中？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.47,0:22:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:22:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.90,0:23:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種距離射擊的光束炮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法打倒這VAL-WALO的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了？
